    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hi friends! I'm parting ways with my favorite ride, and it\u2019s looking for its next big adventure! It\u2019s in really solid shape, runs super smoothly, and has been so reliable for all my daily trips. It\u2019s been well-loved and is totally ready to hit the road with you today. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a great new home!",
